[06/12/2018 21:07:38] <font color="#ffffff">-Erizo.</font>
[06/12/2018 21:07:39] <font color="#ffffff">-Erizo. Vale.</font>
[06/12/2018 21:07:40] <font color="#ffffff">-Cerdo.</font>
[06/12/2018 21:07:42] <font color="#ffffff">-Cerdo.</font>
